text: Pennagaram taluk is a taluk in Dharmapuri district in Tamil Nadu. The headquarters is Pennagaram town. ==Population== 2011 Census states that the total population of this taluk is 234,406 with 123,101 males and 111,305 females. There were 904 females for every 1000 males. ==Reference== Category:Dharmapuri district
title: Pennagaram taluk
